snippet.title: Resident Evil 4 Remake - Extended Gameplay
snippet.description: Here's your first look at extended gameplay from the new Resident Evil 4 remake! The RE4 remake comes to PC, PlayStation, and Xbox consoles on March 24th, 2023.
